    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 130ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[195ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [260ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> couscous</strong> to a heatproof bowl with the <strong>chicken stock</strong>, cover and set aside</p>",
