    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>cucumber</strong> into quarters, lengthways, then chop roughly</p><p>Chop your <strong>baby plum tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>black olives</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
