    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong> and juice of <strong>half </strong>the <strong>lemon[s]</strong> to the chicken and cook for 5-6 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Greek-style chicken</strong></p><p>Note: Please make sure you cook your chicken thoroughly (until there’s no pink meat and it’s piping hot!) as cooking equipment varies</p>",
