    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped cucumber</strong>, <strong>tomatoes</strong> and <strong>olives</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Add the juice of the <strong>remaining lemon</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and give it a good mix up – this is your<strong> chopped salad</strong></p><p>Fluff the <strong>cooked couscous</strong> with a fork then add the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> – this is your <strong>herby couscous</strong></p>",
