      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Greek-style chicken</strong> with the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>salad</strong> and <strong>herby couscous</strong> to the side</p><p>Crumble over your <strong>feta</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
